headline: OGE Energy (OGE) Beats Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: OGE Energy (OGE) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 40.91% and 7.95%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
